dc_title_s: Local Public Health Department Offices, Wisconsin 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents local public health department office sites for Wisconsin in 2020. [This dataset contains the point locations of local health department offices in Wisconsin. Wisconsin local health departments play a central role in providing essential public health services in communities. For more information please visit the Wisconsin Department of Health Services website: https://www.dhs.wisconsin.gov/lh-depts/counties.htm]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data.dhsgis.wi.gov/datasets/8f1e99e30d8e46d9835038a7b1c6e340_1?geometry=-103.830%2C41.874%2C-76.079%2C47.343
